      <hedline>
        <hl1>Should We Stay Or Should We Go?</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Letter from David Fitts calls for national referendum to let Iraqi people decide if American troops should stay or leave (Paul Krugman Aug 6 Op-Ed)</p>
